<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Burkhard Krumm zu Dürrenmungenau</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe einer Kuh des Peter Öttel, Armmann des Friedrich Dürrenloher, Vikar des Heinrich- und Kunigunden-Altars zu St. Sebald.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_368" id="183v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_368_r2l6">Burkharten Krummen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l7">cʒu Dürrenmungnawe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_368_r2l8"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Burkhart / vns hat fürgelegt her fridrıch Durrenloer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l9"><expan>vycar<ex>ier</ex></expan> auf ſant <expan>küng<ex>en</ex></expan> Altar hie in ſant Sebolts pfarre </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Caplan vvie Jr dem Peter Öttell cʒu ſant Peterſgmünd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l11">
<add><ab facs="#facs_368_r1l1"><expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> Armman </ab></add> ein kw genomen habt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Caplan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">dıe </del> Armman <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein kẅ / vnd ob Jr auch ſüſt der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l13"><expan>Armenleute<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> het / das Jr auch vvider <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r2l14">Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_368" id="183v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burkharten Krummen czu Dürrenmungnawe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Burkhart, uns hat fürgelegt her Fridrich
                        Durrenloer, <expan>vycar<ex>ier</ex></expan> auf sant
                            <expan>Küng<ex>en</ex></expan> altar hie in sant Sebolts pfarre,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> caplan, wie ir dem Peter Öttell czu
                        sant Petersgmünd, <add><expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> armman</add>, ein kw
                        genomen habt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> caplan armman
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein kw und, ob ir auch süst der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>armenleute<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        het, das ir auch wider <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                        wöllen etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
